H

handleNotification(data, onNotificationObserver) - Method in class com.bandyer.communication_center.call_client.CallClient
Parses the notification payload provided as first argument. If the payload is in the expected format it will report a new call object and it will notify the observers that an incoming call has been received CallClient.onIncomingCall(incomingCall). Otherwise, if the payload cannot be parsed, or is malformed an error will be reported.
hangUp(reason) - Method in interface com.bandyer.communication_center.call.Call
